  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the study was to evaluate the root canal treatments performed from 1989 to 1995.
      Type of complication, success, new endodontic diseases and number of success were reported.
      Mean clinical parameters were clinical symptoms and presence/absence of apical radiolucency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
